            <p>It gives me great pleasure to comply with your request.</p>

            <p>Enclosed you will find the autograph for your Canadian friend.<ptr target="nyp.00509_n2"/></p>

            <closer>
                <salute rend="right">Yours very truly</salute>
                <signed rend="right">Henry W. Longfellow.</signed>
